freej (0.10git20090824-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * New upstream import.
  * Build-Depend on libcwiid instead of libbluetooth.
  * Build-Depend on libfftw3 instead of fftw3.
  * Add Build-Depend on libsdl-gfx1.2-dev, libx11-dev, liblo0-dev,
    libsamplerate-dev, libcv-dev, libshout-dev, libsdl-ttf2.0-dev,
    libsdl-image1.2-dev, doxygen.
  * Remove doc/scripting make rules as now it is handled by freej itself.
  * Update freej-doc install paths to reflect upstream changes.
  * Remove usr/lib/freej from libfreej0 install path because frei0r is no
    longer shipped.
  * Recommend frei0r-plugins.

 -- Luca Bigliardi <shammash@artha.org>  Mon, 24 Aug 2009 20:02:49 +0100

